<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000704/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Las actividades de Evaluación Continua y Prueba Final seran evaluados bajo los criterios de innovación, proactividad, riesgos en las propuestas, autonomia y liderazgo a la hora de desarrollar y participar en las acticvidades a desarrollar por los alumnos.
The Evaluation Criteria will measure the innovativeness, the proactiveness, the ruisk-taking, the competitive, authonomy and lidership by the alumni on each activity or final evaluation. The online and flipped classes will be encourage using Slack, Miro, Lab Project 2030 and Zoom among others. Consists on a series of theoretical or practical questions, each of which will be done either in or out the classroom time. The syllabus of the classes and exercises will be available in the Artficial Intelligence Gammaapp tool where the material of the subject and the exercises and activities to be developed during the course will be available, link: https://gamma.app/docs/Development-and-Civil-Engineering-Master-Program-prgtlutdwlvnc0c . It will also be taken into account the class participation (in person or online).
Los alumos/as deberan presentar un diario de la asignatura, resolver y participar en las actividades de clase (presenciales o virtuales) y presentar un trabajo por equipos (presencial o online)/Students must present a journal of the subject, solve and participate in class activities (face-to-face or virtual) and present a team work (face-to-face or online).
Las clases, las actividades y los examenes podrán tener cáracter virtual si las circustancias lo exigen o una modalidad mixta si procede. Classes, activities and exams may have a virtual character if the circumstances require it or a mixed modality if applicable."""@es ;
